Rating: 4
As this soup is one of my favorites, I make it all the time. However, an interesting thing happened once when I made it. The soup turned out to be very thick. This is because I burned the onions slightly. Last night, I made it again, with the exact same ingredients as the time before, only I was very careful to not burn the onions. In fact, I undercooked them a little. It is helpful to chop the tomatos as the recipe states ahead of time, instead of as you are making the soup. This was my mistake which burned the onions. Also, the slightly crunchy onions give the soup a nice texture.

