For a hearty version that's good hot or cold with the same wonderful flavors, try this: Saute three medium red or yellow potatoes, chopped, with one medium onion, chopped; 2 garlic cloves, chopped; and a good pinch of red pepper flakes. Add 1 can chicken broth and cook till tender. Then add all the other ingredients and puree with a hand blender. Great with a salad and the ever-popular crusty bread.

